  <source>University Hospitals, Leicester</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether the administration of patient's own bone
      marrow cells into scar areas of the heart, can improve the contractile function of these
      areas.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
